						<a class="post_more_title" href="https://lithub.com/on-writing-the-hospital/">
				<h7 style="display:block;">On Writing the Hospital</h7>
			</a>
			A nurse named Sylvia brought me into the operating room, where she introduced me to two more specialist nurses – I was too stressed...			
			</div>
		</div>
		
